text LittlerootTown_BrendansHouse_1F_EventScript_BrendanGoUpstairs2 {
    format("MOM: See, {PLAYER}? Isn't it nice in here, too?$ The mover's POKéMON do all the work of moving us in and cleaning up after.\l This is so convenient!\p {PLAYER}, your room is upstairs. Go check it out, dear!\p DAD bought you a new clock to mark our move here.\l Don't forget to set it!$ MOM: Well, {PLAYER}?\p Aren't you interested in seeing your very own room?$ MOM: {PLAYER}.\p Go set the clock in your room, honey.$ MOM: Oh! {PLAYER}, {PLAYER}! Quick! Come quickly!$ MOM: Look! It's PETALBURG GYM! Maybe DAD will be on!$ MOM: Oh… It's over.\p I think DAD was on, but we missed him. Too bad.$ Oh, yes. One of DAD's friends lives in town.\p PROF. BIRCH is his name.\p He lives right next door, so you should go over and introduce yourself.$ MOM: See you, honey!$ MOM: Did you introduce yourself to PROF. BIRCH?$ MOM: How are you doing, {PLAYER}? You look a little tired.\p I think you should rest a bit.$ MOM: Take care, honey!$ MOM: Oh? Did DAD give you that BADGE?\p Then here's something from your MOM!$ Don't push yourself too hard, dear. You can always come home.\p Go for it, honey!$ MOM: What is that, honey? A POKéNAV? Someone from DEVON gave it to you?\p Well, honey, how about registering your mom?\p … … …$ Registered MOM in the POKéNAV.$ Fugiiiiih!$ Huggoh, uggo uggo…$ INTERVIEWER: …We brought you this report from in front of PETALBURG GYM.$ There is a movie on TV.\p Two men are dancing on a big piano keyboard.\p Better get going!$ It's the instruction booklet for the RUNNING SHOES.\p “Press the B Button to run while wearing your RUNNING SHOES.\p “Lace up your RUNNING SHOES and hit the road running!”$ DAD: Hm?\p Hey, it's {PLAYER}!\p It's been a while since I saw you, but you look…stronger, somehow.\p That's the impression I get. But your old man hasn't given up yet!\p Oh, yes, I have something for you. This came to you from someone named\l MR. BRINEY.$ DAD: Hm, a TICKET for a ferry?\p If I recall, there are ferry ports in SLATEPORT and LILYCOVE.$ I'd better get back to PETALBURG GYM.\p MOM, thanks for looking after the house while I'm away.$ MOM: That DAD of yours…\p He comes home for the first time in a while, but all he talks about is POKéMON.\p He should relax and stay a little longer.$ MOM: Is that a breaking news story?$ We bring you this emergency news flash!\p In various HOENN locales, there have been reports of a BZZT…colored\l POKéMON in flight.\p The identity of this POKéMON is currently unknown.\p We now return you to the regular movie program.$ MOM: {PLAYER}, did you catch that?\p What color did the announcer say that POKéMON was?$ MOM: Well, isn't that something! There are still unknown POKéMON.")
}

